Author: sigs
Description:
Start your quest by finding boarding pass to Aurora.
https://scoreboard.hf/public/pkg_for_humans.zip
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:
If you found boading pass from pkg, you should be able to use it to connect to WINSHARE on :
aurora.empire.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.20)
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:
From WINSHARE you should have ticket for planet Trantor, find how to use it and go to GOTPASS share on :
trantor.empire.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.10)
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description: If you need Extra point, you can try to find the special dns TXT record from Empire domain.
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:
With your new credentials, dig in the office of the group managing the policies of the Empire domain.
If you find good target information, meet us on c:\
The office door is a share on :
trantor.empire.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.10)
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description: From where you are, you should be able to dump some local citizens credentials and get your prize.
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:
From where you are, find the EmpireSpy user and use his privileges to jump on SPYROOM share on :
trantor.empire.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.10)
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:
In the SPYROOM share, you have all you need to generate you new identity and dump Trantors hashes.
Submit special citizen hash for prize.
trantor.empire.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.10)
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description: Dump citizen's credentials from epsilon.ctf.hf universe. The special citizen hash is your prize.
News: Null

Author: sigs
Description:

If your succeed, your prize is on c:\
compolleron.epsilon.ctf.hf (172.28.20.70)
